Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.43,0:00:15.30,Staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片源\Nchiwa\N\N\N　壓製\N　xelnaga
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.31,0:01:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#05 那些傢伙鬧翻天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.22,0:01:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史托克寫的“吸血鬼”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.53,0:01:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到羅馬尼亞\N當然得買這本書才行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.06,0:01:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也有很多不同版本的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:01:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳姊姊他們真是活力充沛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.12,0:02:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是金先生\N讀仙社的主管
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.49,0:02:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你們是舊書市場裡\N最醒目的三人組
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一眼就認出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.27,0:02:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,0:02:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問工作的內容是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們知道大英圖書館的事件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.87,0:02:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在電視新聞裡看過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四年前發生火災的那個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.68,0:02:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒毀了不少珍藏古書\N是個令人心痛的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細想想\N那只是英國瓦解的序幕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去的榮耀\N現在已經無影無蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在那次火災中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.49,0:02:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說有幾本特別貴重的書\N被帶到國外去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.60,0:02:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼樣的書？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:03:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是一些不對外公開的\N大英圖書館的珍藏書
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的任務\N就是找回其中一本
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.64,0:03:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書名是“脈搏跳動肉之書”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.95,0:03:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪的書名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.65,0:03:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以確認一下內容對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真偽的鑑定由我們來做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那本書被上了鎖\N要處理小組才打得開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些收藏家甚至願意支付\N10億美金買那本書
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在世界上有能力保管的\N只有我們中國的讀仙社
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換句話說就是小偷的小偷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小偷那裡把書偷出來\N讓書得到自由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是正義的一方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是布加勒斯特大學客座教授\N威帕的別墅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他從四年前就住在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:04:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書很有可能在他手中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰調查的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.77,0:04:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們公司的工作人員
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有橋也沒有道路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論是搭船或直昇機\N馬上就會被發現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.84,0:04:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光要靠近就很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚潛入比較安全
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.92,0:04:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待你們的表現囉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.68,0:04:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好﹐我們開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠近外牆的房間\N環境不適合保存書籍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要放的話﹐應該是中央的塔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.47,0:04:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能從監視攝影機的死角\N入侵中庭是最近的路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.10,0:04:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湖面每五分鐘\N會以城堡為中心向外產生波浪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.88,0:04:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是自家發電器的振動嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是覺得這份工作很詭異
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.21,0:04:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是把被偷的書拿回來而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是已經有人在調查了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:05:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼那時候\N不能把書拿回來呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.56,0:05:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是因為沒有\N像我們這種團隊默契
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先潛進去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.46,0:05:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達負責擊退敵人\N瑪姬擔任防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.63,0:05:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟平常一樣的團隊默契\N大家隨機應變吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.57,0:05:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就是走一步算一步嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.84,0:05:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也只有我們姊妹辦得到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願紙保佑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繞到反方向去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:05:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-壞掉了\N-怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.39,0:06:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好險
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授！教授！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到了﹐厄文
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦﹐這可稀奇了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是媒體嗎？還是看熱鬧的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.19,0:06:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是小偷？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.76,0:06:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來好像是操紙師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.73,0:06:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確定嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,0:06:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了啊﹐終於來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.34,0:06:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦呢？教授
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.37,0:06:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還用問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好的…好好的招待之後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我來殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結合力消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.02,0:07:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是受到什麼影響嗎？\N我的弓箭也做不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是可以切割啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.19,0:07:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法\N弓箭和飛鳥就放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪姬使用艾妮達的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個﹐路徑還記得嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.84,0:07:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時折回去比較好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.01,0:07:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在可能已經被發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法回去了啦\N因為無法做飛鳥了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.89,0:07:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被發現\N警報應該早就響了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心﹐只要我們三人合作\N一定還有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核對時間﹐3 2 1 0
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定警備蠻鬆散的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.49,0:08:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪姊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膽子別這麼小啦﹐真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.87,0:08:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？\N竟然有三種聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.47,0:08:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係﹐給我紅酒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.77,0:08:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是拷問房
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.29,0:08:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這會不會是\N金先生說的工作人員？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個都往這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.43,0:09:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要多管閒事！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.53,0:09:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己會保護自己\N不要管我！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.30,0:09:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪姬是為了救妳\N才那麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有幾個人回來呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼﹐是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.08,0:10:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地圖到這裡就沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們覺得是哪條路？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.66,0:10:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.86,0:10:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人分頭找啦\N這樣比較有效率
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.80,0:10:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分開太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險的只有姊姊你們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓箭和飛鳥都不能用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.14,0:10:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和平常一樣.所以沒差
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.81,0:10:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要變成我的絆腳石喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.05,0:10:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達﹐向瑪姬道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點道歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.16,0:10:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊﹐不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:10:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？\N給人添麻煩的是瑪姊耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.66,0:10:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.37,0:11:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.17,0:11:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃去哪裡都好﹐快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪姬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪姊﹐蜜姊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點道歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就去給你們看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打了她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.55,0:11:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是狠心的姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:11:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都要怪我添了麻煩\N才會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪姬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.80,0:12:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麼呢？\N到了這裡以後變得好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情越來越低落
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.77,0:12:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達也是\N她應該不會說那種話的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.54,0:12:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座城堡一定有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.98,0:12:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厄文﹐你有去過倫敦的\N聖保羅大教堂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.69,0:12:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡在走廊的一端\N即便是小小的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都能傳到另一端去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道為什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.77,0:12:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是反射嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.87,0:12:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.04,0:12:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曲狀的牆壁\N會重複反射聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將聲音傳到遙遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經常讓參觀的學生\N嚇得半死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:13:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想回去令人懷念的倫敦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.75,0:13:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的英國
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷喔﹐可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.10,0:13:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有蝙蝠﹐還有狗\N這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是釋放出了\N人類不懂的暗號
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.08,0:13:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊﹐那麼應該是那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空氣在震動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.22,0:13:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.51,0:13:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜姊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到我的實驗場
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美麗的操紙師們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在看哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.98,0:14:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對﹐就是那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.11,0:14:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫威帕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.50,0:14:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是這座城堡的主人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:15:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座城堡的機關\N我已經全部看透了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是味道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你將操縱動物的味道\N散佈在空氣裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.98,0:15:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不記得有散佈出\N那種奇怪的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.19,0:15:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊﹐不對﹐是聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.65,0:15:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.26,0:15:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是對聲音瞭若指掌的專家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.17,0:15:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.33,0:15:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪姬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.67,0:15:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦﹐妳還能動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類能聽見的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.07,0:15:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-姊姊﹐快救艾妮達\N-在20千赫到30千赫之間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.78,0:15:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我能操縱\N在這之上的超音波
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.01,0:15:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及在這之下的低週波
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們凡人雖然聽不見\N但是肉體卻一定會產生反應
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.86,0:15:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非得反應不可
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果用它來製作出某種曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:15:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們覺得會有什麼結果呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:16:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在令人好奇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超音波會讓人情緒焦慮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低週波會促進人的不安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.01,0:16:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用先人的遺產\N由我編出的惡夢樂曲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.81,0:16:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為這樣\N艾妮達跟瑪姬才會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯﹐他們兩人都\N反應得很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.22,0:16:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共振值50
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操紙術對我沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藉由共振的調整
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.43,0:16:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何變化我都能讓它失效
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.16,0:16:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳雖然能巧妙的\N取得情緒上的平衡﹐但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.01,0:16:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.91,0:16:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-姊姊\N-我特製的不協調混音效果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,託你們的福\N我的研究獲得實際驗證了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我要在這裡大喊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操紙師﹐你們被打敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.56,0:17:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是衝著這本書來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.96,0:17:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的竊賊們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡﹐躲到死角裡去了\N不過﹐沒有人可以逃過聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,個別攻擊是贏不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.97,0:17:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定會保護妳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊﹐牛奶糖型還有幾個？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.59,0:17:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們死心啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自殺行為
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢至極﹐去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.84,0:17:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.95,0:18:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能﹐為什麼沒有倒下？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是消音器效果嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭囉嗦的男人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.44,0:18:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共振值0
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.67,0:18:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一本普通的書
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.51,0:18:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厄文﹐閉幕了\N我的演奏結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.89,0:18:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜姊﹐瑪姊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿醉、暈船、暈車\N好像全都一起來的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.69,0:19:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪姊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.76,0:19:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒一醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睜開眼睛啊\N瑪姊﹐妳很強悍的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點小事打不倒妳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪﹐耳膜好像被震破了\N聽不見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是暫時性的﹐馬上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.59,0:19:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.26,0:19:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有沒有受傷？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.43,0:19:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有受傷？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.88,0:20:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起﹐我說妳是絆腳石
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.24,0:20:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起﹐我一副自以為是的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起﹐其實都是你們在保護我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.35,0:20:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起﹐我聽不見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.66,0:20:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.71,0:20:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你要的書\N請確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.33,0:21:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝﹐謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.10,0:21:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後還請多關照喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.07,0:21:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀仙社的工作人員\N桑尼．翁先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人稱“衛生紙交換人”\N那些紙是交換酬勞的用紙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之﹐快點去醫院吧\N瑪姊需要治療
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.06,0:21:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要為教授報仇﹐去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.89,0:21:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.93,0:21:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪姊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.67,0:21:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這槍一定要斃了妳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.11,0:21:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪姊﹐瑪姊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.82,0:21:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的吸血鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.06,0:22:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來\N這位小姐真是勇敢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.56,0:22:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.37,0:22:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她是我引以為傲的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.71,0:22:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.25,0:22:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.22,0:22:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.03,0:22:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛﹐你們這是幹嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.27,0:23:24.14,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍藏的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.21,0:23:30.04,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是凋零散落
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.11,0:23:33.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有和你的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.92,0:23:39.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深烙在我心深處
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.02,0:23:45.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐漸轉涼的海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.06,0:23:51.87,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人嬉戲的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.94,0:23:56.34,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你曬得黝黑的皮膚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.41,0:24:01.74,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,融化在西沉的夕陽裡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.81,0:24:07.22,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願牽著的手永不分離
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.29,0:24:15.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣長大成人該有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.16,0:24:22.22,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在陽光下追逐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.30,0:24:26.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋找你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.37,0:24:33.14,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受到戀情結束的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.21,0:24:37.11,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互依偎


